  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa23">
<l>māri malai muḻaiñcil maṉṉik kiṭantuṟaṅkum</l>
<l>cīriya ciṅkam aṟivuṟṟut tī viḻittu</l>
<l>vēri mayir poṅka veppāṭum pērntutaṟi</l>
<l>mūri nimirntu muḻaṅkip puṟappaṭṭup</l>
<l>pōtarumā pōlē nī pūvaippū vaṇṇā vuṉ</l>
<l>kōyil niṉṟiṅṅaṉē pōntaruḷik kōppuṭaiya</l>
<l>cīriya ciṅkācaṉattiruntu yām vanta</l>
<l>kāriyam ārāyntaruḷēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the excellent lion—which sleeps</l>
<l>settling down in a mountain cave and lying [there during] the rainy season—</l>
<l rend="indent">wakes up from sleep,</l>
<l rend="indent">looks with [its] fire-red eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">moves all around so that its fragrant mane stands on end,</l>
<l rend="indent">shakes [its body]</l>
<l rend="indent">stretches itself,</l>
<l rend="indent">roars,</l>
<l rend="indent">sets forth</l>
<l rend="indent">and comes [out],</l>
<l>O bilberry-flower-hued [Lord]!</l>
<l>Graciously come here from Your palace,</l>
<l>And sitting on the beautiful throne of surpassing excellence,</l>
<l>You grace [us] by looking into the matter for which we have come!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
